name: SRIKANDI
description:
Dewi Srikandi has a strong determination, self-confidence, gentleness, motherhood, and emotion.
Dewi Srikandi is very fond of soldiering and is proficient in using arrow weapons. He got this skill when he studied with Arjuna, who later became her husband
